episodes.description: When spring comes, the Sea of Japan flourishes as plankton reach peak levels. Firefly squid spawn along the shoreline, emitting magical blue light in the surf on nights of the new moon.
episodes.subtitle: Firefly Squid Sparkle in Spring
episodes.title: The Sea of Japan

episodes.description: Frigid winter winds bring stormy weather to the Sea of Japan, but undersea, life flourishes. Shoals of Japanese amberjack migrate to the area, and deep-sea fishes come into the shallows to spawn.
episodes.title: The Sea of Japan
